{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"By birth and by choice,"},{"time":2000,"text":"I've been involved with the auto industry my entire life,"},{"time":5000,"text":"and for the past 30 years,"},{"time":7000,"text":"I've worked at Ford Motor Company."},{"time":9000,"text":"And for most of those years,"},{"time":11000,"text":"I worried about,"},{"time":13000,"text":"how am I going to sell more cars and trucks?"},{"time":15000,"text":"But today I worry about,"},{"time":17000,"text":"what if all we do is sell more cars and trucks?"},{"time":19000,"text":"What happens"},{"time":21000,"text":"when the number of vehicles on the road doubles, triples,"},{"time":24000,"text":"or even quadruples?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":26000,"text":"My life is guided by two great passions,"},{"time":29000,"text":"and the first is automobiles."},{"time":31000,"text":"I literally grew up with the Ford Motor Company."},{"time":33000,"text":"I thought it was so cool as a little boy"},{"time":35000,"text":"when my dad would bring home the latest Ford or Lincoln"},{"time":38000,"text":"and leave it in the driveway."},{"time":40000,"text":"And I decided about that time, about age 10,"},{"time":43000,"text":"that it would be really cool if I was a test driver."},{"time":46000,"text":"So my parents would go to dinner."},{"time":48000,"text":"They'd sit down; I'd sneak out of the house."},{"time":51000,"text":"I'd jump behind the wheel and take the new model around the driveway,"},{"time":54000,"text":"and it was a blast."},{"time":56000,"text":"And that went on for about two years,"},{"time":58000,"text":"until -- I think I was about 12 --"},{"time":60000,"text":"my dad brought home"},{"time":62000,"text":"a Lincoln Mark III."},{"time":64000,"text":"And it was snowing that day."},{"time":66000,"text":"So he and mom went to dinner,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and I snuck out"},{"time":71000,"text":"and thought it'd be really cool to do donuts"},{"time":73000,"text":"or even some figure-eights in the snow."},{"time":75000,"text":"My dad finished dinner early that evening."},{"time":77000,"text":"And he was walking to the front hall"},{"time":79000,"text":"and out the front door"},{"time":81000,"text":"just about the same time I hit some ice"},{"time":83000,"text":"and met him at the front door with the car --"},{"time":86000,"text":"and almost ended up in the front hall."},{"time":88000,"text":"So it kind of cooled my test-driving for a little while."},{"time":91000,"text":"But I really began to love cars then."},{"time":94000,"text":"And my first car was a 1975 electric-green Mustang."},{"time":99000,"text":"And even though the color was pretty hideous,"},{"time":101000,"text":"I did love the car,"},{"time":103000,"text":"and it really cemented my love affair with cars"},{"time":105000,"text":"that's continued on to this day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":108000,"text":"But cars are really more than a passion of mine;"},{"time":111000,"text":"they're quite literally in my blood."},{"time":114000,"text":"My great grandfather was Henry Ford,"},{"time":117000,"text":"and on my mother's side,"},{"time":119000,"text":"my great grandfather was Harvey Firestone."},{"time":121000,"text":"So when I was born,"},{"time":123000,"text":"I guess you could say expectations were kind of high for me."},{"time":127000,"text":"But my great grandfather, Henry Ford,"},{"time":129000,"text":"really believed that the mission of the Ford Motor Company"},{"time":131000,"text":"was to make people's lives better"},{"time":133000,"text":"and make cars affordable so that everyone could have them."},{"time":136000,"text":"Because he believed that with mobility"},{"time":139000,"text":"comes freedom and progress."},{"time":141000,"text":"And that's a belief that I share."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144000,"text":"My other great passion is the environment."},{"time":147000,"text":"And as a young boy, I used to go up to Northern Michigan"},{"time":150000,"text":"and fish in the rivers that Hemingway fished in"},{"time":153000,"text":"and then later wrote about."},{"time":156000,"text":"And it really struck me"},{"time":158000,"text":"as the years went by,"},{"time":160000,"text":"in a very negative way,"},{"time":162000,"text":"when I would go to some stream that I'd loved,"},{"time":164000,"text":"and was used to walking through this field"},{"time":166000,"text":"that was once filled with fireflies,"},{"time":168000,"text":"and now had a strip mall or a bunch of condos on it."},{"time":171000,"text":"And so even at a young age,"},{"time":173000,"text":"that really resonated with me,"},{"time":175000,"text":"and the whole notion of environmental preservation,"},{"time":178000,"text":"at a very basic level, sunk in with me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181000,"text":"As a high-schooler, I started to read"},{"time":183000,"text":"authors like Thoreau and Aldo Leopold"},{"time":186000,"text":"and Edward Abbey,"},{"time":188000,"text":"and I really began to develop"},{"time":190000,"text":"a deeper appreciation of the natural world."},{"time":193000,"text":"But it never really occurred to me"},{"time":195000,"text":"that my love of cars and trucks"},{"time":199000,"text":"would ever be in conflict with nature."},{"time":202000,"text":"And that was true"},{"time":204000,"text":"until I got to college."},{"time":206000,"text":"And when I got to college, you can imagine my surprise"},{"time":209000,"text":"when I would go to class"},{"time":211000,"text":"and a number of my professors would say"},{"time":214000,"text":"that Ford Motor Company and my family"},{"time":216000,"text":"was everything that was wrong with our country."},{"time":220000,"text":"They thought that we were more interested, as an industry,"},{"time":223000,"text":"in profits, rather than progress,"},{"time":225000,"text":"and that we filled the skies with smog --"},{"time":229000,"text":"and frankly, we were the enemy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"I joined Ford after college,"},{"time":233000,"text":"after some soul searching"},{"time":235000,"text":"whether or not this is really the right thing to do."},{"time":238000,"text":"But I decided that I wanted to go"},{"time":240000,"text":"and see if I could affect change there."},{"time":242000,"text":"And as I look back over 30 years ago,"},{"time":245000,"text":"it was a little naive to think at that age"},{"time":247000,"text":"that I could. But I wanted to."},{"time":249000,"text":"And I really discovered"},{"time":251000,"text":"that my professors weren't completely wrong."},{"time":253000,"text":"In fact, when I got back to Detroit,"},{"time":255000,"text":"my environmental leanings weren't exactly embraced"},{"time":258000,"text":"by those in my own company,"},{"time":260000,"text":"and certainly by those in the industry."},{"time":262000,"text":"I had some very interesting conversations,"},{"time":264000,"text":"as you can imagine."},{"time":266000,"text":"There were some within Ford"},{"time":268000,"text":"who believed that all this ecological nonsense"},{"time":271000,"text":"should just disappear"},{"time":273000,"text":"and that I needed to stop hanging out"},{"time":275000,"text":"with \"environmental wackos.\""},{"time":278000,"text":"I was considered a radical."},{"time":280000,"text":"And I'll never forget the day I was called in by a member of top management"},{"time":283000,"text":"and told to stop associating"},{"time":285000,"text":"with any known or suspected environmentalists."},{"time":288000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":292000,"text":"Of course, I had no intention of doing that,"},{"time":295000,"text":"and I kept speaking out about the environment,"},{"time":297000,"text":"and it really was the topic"},{"time":299000,"text":"that we now today call sustainability."},{"time":301000,"text":"And in time, my views went from controversial"},{"time":304000,"text":"to more or less consensus today."},{"time":306000,"text":"I mean, I think most people in the industry"},{"time":308000,"text":"understand that we've got to get on with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"And the good news is today we are tackling the big issues,"},{"time":313000,"text":"of cars and the environment --"},{"time":315000,"text":"not only at Ford, but really as an industry."},{"time":318000,"text":"We're pushing fuel efficiency to new heights."},{"time":321000,"text":"And with new technology,"},{"time":323000,"text":"we're reducing -- and I believe, someday we'll eliminate --"},{"time":326000,"text":"CO2 emissions."},{"time":328000,"text":"We're starting to sell electric cars, which is great."},{"time":331000,"text":"We're developing alternative powertrains"},{"time":333000,"text":"that are going to make cars affordable"},{"time":335000,"text":"in every sense of the word --"},{"time":338000,"text":"economically, socially"},{"time":340000,"text":"and environmentally."},{"time":342000,"text":"And actually, although we've got a long way to go"},{"time":344000,"text":"and a lot of work to do,"},{"time":346000,"text":"I can see the day where my two great passions --"},{"time":349000,"text":"cars and the environment --"},{"time":351000,"text":"actually come into harmony."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353000,"text":"But unfortunately,"},{"time":355000,"text":"as we're on our way to solving one monstrous problem --"},{"time":357000,"text":"and as I said, we're not there yet; we've got a lot of work to do,"},{"time":360000,"text":"but I can see where we will --"},{"time":362000,"text":"but even as we're in the process of doing that,"},{"time":365000,"text":"another huge problem is looming,"},{"time":367000,"text":"and people aren't noticing."},{"time":370000,"text":"And that is the freedom of mobility"},{"time":372000,"text":"that my great grandfather brought to people"},{"time":374000,"text":"is now being threatened, just as the environment is."},{"time":377000,"text":"The problem, put in its simplest terms,"},{"time":380000,"text":"is one of mathematics."},{"time":382000,"text":"Today there are approximately 6.8 billion people in the world,"},{"time":386000,"text":"and within our lifetime, that number's going to grow"},{"time":388000,"text":"to about nine billion."},{"time":390000,"text":"And at that population level,"},{"time":392000,"text":"our planet will be dealing with the limits of growth."},{"time":395000,"text":"And with that growth"},{"time":397000,"text":"comes some severe practical problems,"},{"time":400000,"text":"one of which is our transportation system"},{"time":403000,"text":"simply won't be able to deal with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":406000,"text":"When we look at the population growth in terms of cars,"},{"time":408000,"text":"it becomes even clearer."},{"time":410000,"text":"Today there are about 800 million cars on the road worldwide."},{"time":413000,"text":"But with more people"},{"time":415000,"text":"and greater prosperity around the world,"},{"time":417000,"text":"that number's going to grow"},{"time":419000,"text":"to between two and four billion cars by mid century."},{"time":422000,"text":"And this is going to create the kind of global gridlock"},{"time":425000,"text":"that the world has never seen before."},{"time":428000,"text":"Now think about the impact"},{"time":430000,"text":"that this is going to have on our daily lives."},{"time":432000,"text":"Today the average American"},{"time":434000,"text":"spends about a week a year"},{"time":436000,"text":"stuck in traffic jams,"},{"time":438000,"text":"and that's a huge waste of time and resources."},{"time":441000,"text":"But that's nothing compared"},{"time":443000,"text":"to what's going on"},{"time":445000,"text":"in the nations that are growing the fastest."},{"time":447000,"text":"Today the average driver in Beijing"},{"time":449000,"text":"has a five-hour commute."},{"time":452000,"text":"And last summer -- many of you probably saw this --"},{"time":455000,"text":"there was a hundred-mile traffic jam"},{"time":458000,"text":"that took 11 days to clear in China."},{"time":461000,"text":"In the decades to come,"},{"time":463000,"text":"75 percent of the world's population"},{"time":465000,"text":"will live in cities,"},{"time":467000,"text":"and 50 of those cities"},{"time":469000,"text":"will be of 10 million people or more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472000,"text":"So you can see the size of the issue that we're facing."},{"time":475000,"text":"When you factor in population growth,"},{"time":478000,"text":"it's clear that the mobility model that we have today"},{"time":481000,"text":"simply will not work tomorrow."},{"time":483000,"text":"Frankly, four billion clean cars on the road"},{"time":486000,"text":"are still four billion cars,"},{"time":488000,"text":"and a traffic jam with no emissions"},{"time":491000,"text":"is still a traffic jam."},{"time":494000,"text":"So, if we make no changes today,"},{"time":497000,"text":"what does tomorrow look like?"},{"time":499000,"text":"Well I think you probably already have the picture."},{"time":502000,"text":"Traffic jams are just a symptom of this challenge,"},{"time":504000,"text":"and they're really very, very inconvenient,"},{"time":506000,"text":"but that's all they are."},{"time":508000,"text":"But the bigger issue"},{"time":510000,"text":"is that global gridlock"},{"time":512000,"text":"is going to stifle economic growth"},{"time":514000,"text":"and our ability to deliver"},{"time":516000,"text":"food and health care,"},{"time":518000,"text":"particularly to people that live in city centers."},{"time":521000,"text":"And our quality of life is going to be severely compromised."},{"time":525000,"text":"So what's going to solve this?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":527000,"text":"Well the answer isn't going to be more of the same."},{"time":530000,"text":"My great grandfather once said"},{"time":533000,"text":"before he invented the Model T,"},{"time":535000,"text":"\"If I had asked people then what they wanted,"},{"time":537000,"text":"they would have answered,"},{"time":539000,"text":"'We want faster horses.'\""},{"time":541000,"text":"So the answer to more cars"},{"time":543000,"text":"is simply not to have more roads."},{"time":546000,"text":"When America began moving west,"},{"time":548000,"text":"we didn't add more wagon trains,"},{"time":550000,"text":"we built railroads."},{"time":552000,"text":"And to connect our country after World War II,"},{"time":554000,"text":"we didn't build more two-lane highways,"},{"time":557000,"text":"we built the interstate highway system."},{"time":559000,"text":"Today we need that same leap in thinking"},{"time":562000,"text":"for us to create a viable future."},{"time":565000,"text":"We are going to build smart cars,"},{"time":567000,"text":"but we also need to build"},{"time":569000,"text":"smart roads, smart parking,"},{"time":571000,"text":"smart public transportation systems and more."},{"time":574000,"text":"We don't want to waste our time"},{"time":576000,"text":"sitting in traffic, sitting at tollbooths"},{"time":578000,"text":"or looking for parking spots."},{"time":581000,"text":"We need an integrated system"},{"time":583000,"text":"that uses real time data"},{"time":585000,"text":"to optimize personal mobility on a massive scale"},{"time":588000,"text":"without hassle or compromises for travelers."},{"time":591000,"text":"And frankly, that's the kind of system"},{"time":593000,"text":"that's going to make the future of personal mobility sustainable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597000,"text":"Now the good news is some of this work has already begun"},{"time":600000,"text":"in different parts of the world."},{"time":602000,"text":"The city of Masdar in Abu Dhabi"},{"time":605000,"text":"uses driverless electric vehicles"},{"time":607000,"text":"that can communicate with one another,"},{"time":609000,"text":"and they go underneath the city streets."},{"time":612000,"text":"And up above, you've got a series of pedestrian walkways."},{"time":615000,"text":"On New York City's 34th Street,"},{"time":617000,"text":"gridlock will soon be replaced"},{"time":619000,"text":"with a connected system"},{"time":621000,"text":"of vehicle-specific corridors."},{"time":624000,"text":"Pedestrian zones and dedicated traffic lanes are going to be created,"},{"time":627000,"text":"and all of this will cut down the average rush hour commute"},{"time":630000,"text":"to get across town in New York"},{"time":632000,"text":"from about an hour today at rush hour"},{"time":634000,"text":"to about 20 minutes."},{"time":636000,"text":"Now if you look at Hong Kong,"},{"time":638000,"text":"they have a very interesting system called Octopus there."},{"time":641000,"text":"It's a system that really ties together"},{"time":643000,"text":"all the transportation assets"},{"time":645000,"text":"into a single payment system."},{"time":647000,"text":"So parking garages, buses, trains,"},{"time":650000,"text":"they all operate within the same system."},{"time":653000,"text":"Now shared car services"},{"time":655000,"text":"are also springing up around the world,"},{"time":657000,"text":"and these efforts, I think, are great."},{"time":659000,"text":"They're relieving congestion,"},{"time":661000,"text":"and they're frankly starting to save some fuel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":663000,"text":"These are all really good ideas"},{"time":665000,"text":"that will move us forward."},{"time":667000,"text":"But what really inspires me"},{"time":669000,"text":"is what's going to be possible"},{"time":671000,"text":"when our cars can begin talking to each other."},{"time":673000,"text":"Very soon, the same systems that we use today"},{"time":676000,"text":"to bring music and entertainment"},{"time":678000,"text":"and GPS information into our vehicles"},{"time":681000,"text":"are going to be used to create"},{"time":683000,"text":"a smart vehicle network."},{"time":685000,"text":"Every morning I drive about 30 miles"},{"time":687000,"text":"from my home in Ann Arbor to my office in Dearborn, Michigan."},{"time":690000,"text":"And every night I go home,"},{"time":692000,"text":"my commute is a total crapshoot."},{"time":694000,"text":"And I often have to leave the freeway"},{"time":696000,"text":"and look for different ways"},{"time":698000,"text":"for me to try and make it home."},{"time":700000,"text":"But very soon we're going to see the days"},{"time":702000,"text":"when cars are essentially talking to each other."},{"time":705000,"text":"So if the car ahead of me on I-94 hits traffic,"},{"time":708000,"text":"it will immediately alert my car"},{"time":711000,"text":"and tell my car to reroute itself"},{"time":713000,"text":"to get me home in the best possible way."},{"time":716000,"text":"And these systems are being tested right now,"},{"time":718000,"text":"and frankly they're going to be ready for prime time pretty soon."}]},{"cues":[{"time":722000,"text":"But the potential of a connected car network"},{"time":725000,"text":"is almost limitless."},{"time":727000,"text":"So just imagine:"},{"time":729000,"text":"one day very soon,"},{"time":731000,"text":"you're going to be able to plan a trip downtown"},{"time":733000,"text":"and your car will be connected to a smart parking system."},{"time":736000,"text":"So you get in your car,"},{"time":738000,"text":"and as you get in your car,"},{"time":740000,"text":"your car will reserve you a parking spot before you arrive --"},{"time":743000,"text":"no more driving around looking for one,"},{"time":745000,"text":"which frankly is one of the biggest users of fuel"},{"time":748000,"text":"in today's cars in urban areas --"},{"time":750000,"text":"is looking for parking spots."},{"time":752000,"text":"Or think about being in New York City"},{"time":754000,"text":"and tracking down an intelligent cab on your smart phone"},{"time":757000,"text":"so you don't have to wait in the cold to hail one."},{"time":761000,"text":"Or being at a future TED Conference"},{"time":763000,"text":"and having your car"},{"time":765000,"text":"talk to the calendars of everybody here"},{"time":767000,"text":"and telling you all the best route to take home"},{"time":769000,"text":"and when you should leave"},{"time":771000,"text":"so that you can all arrive at your next destination on time."},{"time":774000,"text":"This is the kind of technology"},{"time":776000,"text":"that will merge millions of individual vehicles"},{"time":779000,"text":"into a single system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":781000,"text":"So I think it's clear we have the beginnings of a solution"},{"time":784000,"text":"to this enormous problem."},{"time":787000,"text":"But as we found out with addressing CO2 issues,"},{"time":790000,"text":"and also fossil fuels,"},{"time":792000,"text":"there is no one silver bullet."},{"time":794000,"text":"The solution is not going to be"},{"time":796000,"text":"more cars, more roads or a new rail system;"},{"time":799000,"text":"it can only be found, I believe,"},{"time":801000,"text":"in a global network"},{"time":803000,"text":"of interconnected solutions."},{"time":805000,"text":"Now I know we can develop the technology"},{"time":807000,"text":"that's going to make this work,"},{"time":809000,"text":"but we've got to be willing to get out there"},{"time":811000,"text":"and seek out the solutions --"},{"time":813000,"text":"whether that means vehicle sharing or public transportation"},{"time":816000,"text":"or some other way we haven't even thought of yet;"},{"time":819000,"text":"our overall transportation-mix and infrastructure"},{"time":822000,"text":"must support all the future options."}]},{"cues":[{"time":825000,"text":"We need our best and our brightest"},{"time":827000,"text":"to start entertaining this issue."},{"time":829000,"text":"Companies, entrepreneurs, venture capitalists,"},{"time":832000,"text":"they all need to understand"},{"time":834000,"text":"this is a huge business opportunity,"},{"time":836000,"text":"as well as an enormous social problem."},{"time":838000,"text":"And just as these groups"},{"time":840000,"text":"embrace the green energy challenge --"},{"time":843000,"text":"and it's really been amazing to me to watch"},{"time":845000,"text":"how much brain power, how much money"},{"time":848000,"text":"and how much serious thought"},{"time":850000,"text":"has, really over the last three years,"},{"time":852000,"text":"just poured into the green energy field."},{"time":854000,"text":"We need that same kind of passion and energy"},{"time":857000,"text":"to attack global gridlock."},{"time":859000,"text":"But we need people like all of you in this room,"},{"time":861000,"text":"leading thinkers."},{"time":863000,"text":"I mean, frankly, I need all of you"},{"time":865000,"text":"to think about how"},{"time":867000,"text":"you can help solve this huge issue."},{"time":869000,"text":"And we need people from all walks of life;"},{"time":871000,"text":"not just inventors, we need policymakers"},{"time":873000,"text":"and government officials"},{"time":875000,"text":"to also think about how they're going to respond to this challenge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":878000,"text":"This isn't going to be solved"},{"time":880000,"text":"by any one person or one group."},{"time":882000,"text":"It's going to really require a national energy policy,"},{"time":885000,"text":"frankly for each country,"},{"time":887000,"text":"because the solutions in each country are going to be different"},{"time":890000,"text":"based upon income levels, traffic jams"},{"time":893000,"text":"and also how integrated"},{"time":895000,"text":"the systems already are."},{"time":897000,"text":"But we need to get going, and we need to get going today."},{"time":900000,"text":"And we must have an infrastructure"},{"time":902000,"text":"that's designed to support"},{"time":904000,"text":"this flexible future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":906000,"text":"You know, we've come a long way."},{"time":908000,"text":"Since the Model T,"},{"time":910000,"text":"most people never traveled"},{"time":912000,"text":"more than 25 miles from home in their entire lifetime."},{"time":915000,"text":"And since then,"},{"time":917000,"text":"the automobile has allowed us the freedom"},{"time":919000,"text":"to choose where we live, where we work,"},{"time":921000,"text":"where we play"},{"time":923000,"text":"and frankly when we just go out and want to move around."},{"time":926000,"text":"We don't want to regress and lose that freedom."},{"time":929000,"text":"We're on our way to solving --"},{"time":931000,"text":"and as I said earlier, I know we've got a long way to go --"},{"time":933000,"text":"the one big issue that we're all focused on that threatens it,"},{"time":936000,"text":"and that's the environmental issue,"},{"time":938000,"text":"but I believe we all must turn"},{"time":940000,"text":"all of our effort and all of our ingenuity and determination"},{"time":944000,"text":"to help now solve this notion of global gridlock."},{"time":947000,"text":"Because in doing so,"},{"time":949000,"text":"we're going to preserve what we've really come to take for granted,"},{"time":952000,"text":"which is the freedom to move"},{"time":954000,"text":"and move very effortlessly around the world."},{"time":957000,"text":"And it frankly will enhance our quality of life"},{"time":959000,"text":"if we fix this."},{"time":961000,"text":"Because, if you can envision, as I do,"},{"time":964000,"text":"a future of zero emissions"},{"time":966000,"text":"and freedom to move around the country and around the world"},{"time":969000,"text":"like we take for granted today,"},{"time":971000,"text":"that's worth the hard work today"},{"time":973000,"text":"to preserve that for tomorrow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":975000,"text":"I believe we're at our best"},{"time":977000,"text":"when we're confronted with big issues."},{"time":979000,"text":"This is a big one, and it won't wait."},{"time":981000,"text":"So let's get started now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":983000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":985000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}